title: NAPLAN validation schema
description: Schema for validating student registrations for NAPLAN SRM

ASLSchoolId.title: ASLSchoolId schema.
ASLSchoolId.description: All students must be associated with a valid ASL ID.
ASLSchoolId.name: ASLSchoolId

BirthDate.title: BirthDate schema.
BirthDate.description: Date of Birth for this student.
BirthDate.name: BirthDate

DiocesanId.title: DiocesanId schema.
DiocesanId.description: A student identifier applied by a diocese.
DiocesanId.name: DiocesanId

FFPOS.title: FFPOS schema.
FFPOS.description: Is this a Full Fee Paying Student.
FFPOS.name: FFPOS

JurisdictionId.title: JurisdictionId schema.
JurisdictionId.description: Student Id assigned by jurisdiction, such as a state-level ID.
JurisdictionId.name: JurisdictionId

LocalId.title: LocalId schema.
LocalId.description: The student id assigned by and used by local school administrative system. Ideally a persistent Local Student Identifier from source system.  Assumed this will be local per school Student Information System.
LocalId.name: LocalId

NationalId.title: NationalId schema.
NationalId.description: Placeholder for a Nationally persistent Student Identifier.
NationalId.name: NationalId

OtherId.title: OtherId schema.
OtherId.description: Any other Student Identifier deemed useful for NAPLAN purposes.
OtherId.name: OtherId

PreviousJurisdictionId.title: PreviousJurisdictionId schema.
PreviousJurisdictionId.description: Student Id assigned by jurisdiction, such as a state-level ID, for this student in a previous cycle of NAPLAN.
PreviousJurisdictionId.name: JurisdictionId

SectorId.title: SectorId schema.
SectorId.description: An identifier applied by a school sector
SectorId.name: SectorId

StateProvinceId.title: StateProvinceId schema.
StateProvinceId.description: An identifier which is applied state wide. Persistent Jurisdiction Student Identifier e.g. VSN for VIC; in this case, the Id may be only for the purposes of NAPLAN.
StateProvinceId.name: StateProvinceId

TAAId.title: TAAId schema.
TAAId.description: An identifier assigned by and used by TAA for NAPLAN processing.
TAAId.name: TAAId
